ygData.subject: Re: I need some tips
ygData.msgSnippet: As far as hunting, I don t see why you should have any problems hunting. Just go to Lake of Ill Omens and then shout out level 13 sk lfg (looking for group).
ygData.messageBody:
As far as hunting, I don't see why you should
have any problems hunting. Just go to Lake of Ill
Omens and then shout out level 13 sk lfg (looking for
group). You shouldn't have much problem finding a
group.<br><br>Hunting is good in Lake as spawn rates seem swift and
fast. Haven't personally killed there much as I went
the Derv camp, Orcs in Oasis, and Aviaks route. Had
been doing Tech Mas Gnolls but friends told me to go
to Lake. Lake doesn't seem to have much loot but
dang the exp is goooood and the stream of kills rarely
pauses.<br><br>Hope that helped.<br>shooman out
